window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Actor, singer...necromancer?</b></p> <p>All the world's a stage...even when you're teleported to a new world.</p> <p>Struggling actress Cara O'Sullivan was walking down the street of Galway one moment, and the next, she was in an ancient tomb in a faraway world. Alone in the dark with her cell phone as her last tenuous connection to home, Cara sings her favorite song. To her astonishment, her song casts a spell of light into the world...and from the depths, something hears her. Challenged by a ghostly knight, a tragic necromancer, and hordes of undead, can a young woman who does not believe in heroes become one herself?</p>"; 
